To start the container:
docker run -d -it --name websearch ubuntu sh -c 'echo "Input website:"; read website; echo "Searching..."; sleep 1; curl http://$website;'

To exec inside the container:
docker exec -it websearch bash

Inside the container:
apt update
apt install curl

Back outside of the container:
docker attach websearch

And now typing a web address in the prompt will print the html of that website.
